</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/18iHR5hbMYo" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/09/future-apple-silicon-macs-will-reportedly-use-3nm-chips-with-up-to-40-cores/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=future-apple-silicon-macs-will-reportedly-use-3nm-chips-with-up-to-40-cores</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>試駕 Model Y 長續航版，香港首個 TESLA FEST 展覽 + 體驗 Art Jamming 活動</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/2WIv_dqjblI/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[arthur]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 09 Nov 2021 07:43:36 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><category><![CDATA[EV]]></category><category><![CDATA[Model Y]]></category><category><![CDATA[Tesla]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1070379</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Tesla 於 2021 年 11 月 8 日至 14 號於亞洲國際博覽館 5 號展館舉行首次香港舉辦的 TESLA [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Tesla 於 2021 年 11 月 8 日至 14 號於亞洲國際博覽館 5 號展館舉行首次香港舉辦的 TESLA FEST 及 Model Y Long Range 長續航版本試駕活動。在活動中，參加者不但可以率先於特別設計路線試駕最新抵港的 Model Y 長續航版本，更可以在會場中參加一眾攤位市集及兒童駕駛學院。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1070386 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_181345-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_181345-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_181345-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_181345-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_181345-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_181345-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_181345-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1070380 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_163127-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_163127-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_163127-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_163127-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_163127-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_163127-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_163127-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1070384 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180413-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180413-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180413-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180413-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180413-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180413-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180413-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1070383 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180403-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180403-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180403-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180403-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180403-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180403-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180403-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">活動期間會有不同品牌參與，包括皮革製作、花飾設計、香氛蠟燭甚至消毒和露營用品，你可以在試駕完畢後，到市集休息和閒逛。另外，場內有兩條特別試駕路線，讓兒童駕著滑行車 Model Y 和首部配備 Tesla 電池的兒童電動車 Model S ，感受 TESLA FEST 的歡樂氣氛。TESLA FEST 由即日起至 11 月 14 日於亞洲博覽館 5 號館舉行，參加者可於 Tesla 香港官方網頁率先登記或直接入場。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1070381 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_163939-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_163939-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_163939-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_163939-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_163939-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_163939-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_163939-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1070385 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180454-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180454-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180454-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180454-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180454-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180454-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_180454-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1070382 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_170117-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_170117-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_170117-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_170117-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_170117-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_170117-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/20211108_170117-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Model Y 是 Tesla 首部大眾化的多用途 SUV，新登場的 Long Range 版本配備全輪驅動雙摩打，由靜止加速至時速 100 公里只需 5.1 秒，同時具備高達 542 公里 (WLTP) 的續航距離。</p><p><img class="aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0x0-Family_03-1280x853.jpg" /></p><p><img class="aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1.png" /></p></p><div class="feedflare">
